Package org.eMayor.ServiceHandling.PrintingUtility.ejb

Class Summary
HTMLPrinter Prints text, HTML and RTF documents by rendered in a JEditorPane by the appropriate EditorKit.
MyHTMLEditorKit Subclasses javax.swing.text.html.HTMLEditorKit to allow for
complete rendering of an HTMLDocument's images
by using MyHTMLEditorKit.MyHTMLFactory
MyHTMLEditorKit.MyHTMLFactory Subclasses javax.swing.text.html.HTMLEditorKit.HTMLFactory to allow for
complete rendering of an HTMLDocument's images
by using MyImageView
MyImageView Subclasses javax.swing.text.View to allow for
complete rendering of an HTMLDocument's images
PrintAttributeListener Reports attribute changes in the monitored PrintService
PrinterBean  
PrintingUtility Prints TEXT, HTML, RTF, GIF, JPEG, PCL, PDF, POSTSCRIPT
TEXT, HTML, RTF are printed as rendered by JEditorPane
PrintPreviewDialog Creates a Print Preview window allowing the user to accept or cancel the printing
PrintServiceJobListener Reports attribute changes in the monitored PrintJob
